### User Management Features (Super Users Only)

#### Adding New Users
1. Navigate to User Management page
2. Click "Add User" button
3. Fill in required information:
   - Full Name
   - Username (must be unique)
   - Email address
   - Password (can be generated automatically)
4. Assign roles (multiple roles allowed)
5. Assign tools (multiple tools allowed)
6. Set account status (Active/Inactive)
7. Option to send credentials via email

#### Editing Existing Users
1. Navigate to User Management page
2. Find user in the table
3. Click the Edit button (pencil icon)
4. Modify user information:
   - Full Name
   - Email address
   - Role assignments
   - Tool assignments
   - Account status
5. Save changes

#### Deleting Users
1. Navigate to User Management page
2. Find user in the table
3. Click the Delete button (trash icon)
4. Confirm deletion
5. User is permanently removed from system

