### Login Process
1. Navigate to http://localhost:2005/login
2. Enter username and password
3. Click "Sign In"
4. System validates credentials
5. Upon success, redirected to dashboard
6. JWT token stored for session management

### Password Reset
- Password reset functionality available on login page
- Click "Reset Password" link
- Follow email instructions (when email service is configured)

### System Requirements
- Modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)
