### Troubleshooting

#### Cannot Login
- Verify username and password are correct
- Check if account is active
- Contact system administrator

#### Cannot Access User Management
- Verify user has Super User role
- Check role assignments in database
- Contact system administrator

#### API Connection Issues
- Check if backend service is running (port 2003)
- Verify network connectivity
- Check browser console for errors

### Technical Information

#### Backend API
- Base URL: http://localhost:2003
- Authentication: Bearer token (JWT)
- Endpoints:
  - POST `/api/v1/auth/login` - User login
  - GET `/api/v1/users` - List all users
  - POST `/api/v1/users` - Create new user
  - PUT `/api/v1/users/{id}` - Update user
  - DELETE `/api/v1/users/{id}` - Delete user
  - GET `/api/v1/users/roles` - Get all roles
  - GET `/api/v1/users/tools` - Get all tools

#### Frontend Application
- Technology: Next.js (React framework)
- Port: 2004 (direct), 2005 (via nginx proxy)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS
- State Management: React hooks

#### Database
- Type: PostgreSQL
- Port: 2001
- Tables: users, roles, tools, user_roles, user_tools

